*** ******** ******** ** *** **** ******* * **** ********* *** ******* *** **** *** ********* *** **** *** ** ***** **** *** ******** ** ********** I had visited for Root canol. He explained the diagnosis and the cure very patiently and kept updating me every step of the way. His staff is also very prompt, polite and helpful in scheduling or re- scheduling your appointments. Overall a big thumbs up to Dr. Shailesh Rojekar and his setup. All the best for Prudental Clinic....!!

Impressed with the general upkeep  & ambience of the clinic  . Doctor’ s explanation of the dental issue , various options available , approximate estimate of the treatment & timeline is noteworthy.Doctor’s post graduate stint at the prestigious University college , London increased confidence in his abilities. Overall good experience .
- Area for improvement: 
 1. Filling of the history form is little time consuming . Can be done either on iPad or in advance by email. 
2. Time to replace the  rickety lift at Rajan House or keep a lift man . Opening  & closing the manual doors of the lift  is quite a task. 
3. Ground floor entry  has few steps. It would help if on both sides handle bars are fitted on the wall for support .

The experience with Dr. Shailesh and Dr. Supriya Rojakar has been extremely satisfying. They are both, attentive, professional *** ****** ******** I have been consulting them for the past few years, for initial repair and treatment followed by regular follow-up and maintenance, and have not experienced any dental complaints since starting off under their care. Highly sophisticated treatment techniques, an inviting clinic and their own warmth and attentiveness make the visits a very pleasant, pain-free and soothing experience...quite unlike any other dentists’ visits.
Doctor did an intricate root canal on a very difficult tooth. Very professional approach. Clinic is very clean. Uses state of the art technology. Staff is friendly. Highly recommend.
